Content: Update your trailer's appearance with chrome finish ABS hub covers that offer the best retention system of any on the market today. The Versa-Lok patented locking system locks onto the wheel with a simple twist, allowing easy access to your trailer wheel hubs without prying them off. No tools needed for installation or removal....
